# Privacy Policy – Ceibo Apps

**Last Updated:** January 28, 2026

At **Ceibo Apps**, we respect your privacy. This policy explains how our applications handle your data.

---

### Table of Contents
1. [Data Collection by Ceibo Apps](#1-data-collection-by-ceibo-apps)
2. [Device Permissions](#2-device-permissions)
