## 1. Data Collection by Ceibo Apps
Applications published by Ceibo Apps are designed with a **privacy-first** approach. Our apps:

* **Do not** require user accounts.
* **Do not** include advertising.
* **Do not** use analytics or tracking technologies.
* **Do not** communicate with external servers operated by Ceibo Apps.

All application functionality operates **locally** on your device. We do not collect, store, transmit, or share personal or sensitive user data.

## 2. Device Permissions
If an app requests device permissions (such as camera, microphone, storage, or audio access), these permissions are used **solely** to provide the app’s core functionality. 

No data accessed through these permissions is collected, stored, or transmitted by Ceibo Apps. We do not share any data with third parties.

## 3. Third-Party Services (Google Play)
Apps by Ceibo Apps are distributed through the **Google Play Store**. 

Purchases, downloads, and billing are processed by Google and are subject to Google’s privacy policies. Google may independently collect information for payment processing, fraud prevention, and legal compliance, including:
* Purchase and transaction details
* Device information
* Country or region

Ceibo Apps does not have access to, control over, or responsibility for data collected directly by Google. For more information, please review:
* [Google Privacy Policy](https://policies.google.com/privacy)
* [Google Play & Google Payments Privacy Notices](https://payments.google.com/payments/apis-secure/u/0/get_legal_document?ldo=0&ldt=privacynotice)

## 4. Changes to This Privacy Policy
If this Privacy Policy is updated, the revised version will be made available at the hosting URL or within the application. Continued use of the app constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.

## 5. Contact
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, you may contact:

**Email:** [ceiboapps@proton.me](mailto:ceiboapps@proton.me)
